              THRU  S3200-TKJLR003-FETCH-EXT

           PERFORM  UNTIL  EOF-Y

                    PERFORM  S3300-DATA-MOVE-RTN
                       THRU  S3300-DATA-MOVE-EXT

                    PERFORM  S3400-DATA-WRITE-RTN
                       THRU  S3400-DATA-WRITE-EXT

                    PERFORM  S3200-TKJLR003-FETCH-RTN
                       THRU  S3200-TKJLR003-FETCH-EXT
           END-PERFORM

           PERFORM  S3400-TKJLR003-CLOSE-RTN
              THRU  S3400-TKJLR003-CLOSE-EXT
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
